ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (South Slave / North Slave Regions) Order
PrecisOrder (1) repealing the existing Order Respecting the Withdrawal from Disposal of Certain Lands in the Northwest Territories (Akaitcho Dene First Nations, N.W.T.), made by Order in Council P.C. 2007-1661 of November 1, 2007 and (2) making a new WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (South Slave/North Slave Regions) ORDER in order to facilitate the resolution of Aboriginal land and resource agreements.
